    public class LumberingBrute
extends Zombie
    The Class Lumbering Brute. The slow and steady zombie has a speed of 10 units. The zombie does 50 damage so it can kill almost any plant in a single turn. The zombie has 700 health so it will take a long time for a SEED_SPITTER to kill it.
    Author:
    Ian Wong
